## 🐛 Bug Report

Lib version: 4.2.1

1. workbook.addImage 添加 img1, img2
2. worksheet.addImage 按[img2, img1, img1]的顺序添加3张图片
3. 第3张图片应该是img2，但是序列化后变为img1

## Steps To Reproduce

```javascript
const workbook = new ExcelJs.Workbook()

  const img1 = workbook.addImage({filename: '1.png', extension: 'png'})
  const img2 = workbook.addImage({filename: '2.png', extension: 'png'})

  const sheet = workbook.addWorksheet()
  sheet.addImage(img2, 'A1:A1')
  sheet.addImage(img1, 'A3:A3')
  sheet.addImage(img1, 'A5:A5')
  sheet.getRow(5).getCell(2).value = 'image wrong'

  await workbook.xlsx.writeFile('bug.xlsx')
```

## Possible solution

worksheet-xform.js  line: 223-257

```javascript
    // bugfix modify
    // let rIdImage =
